<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=100854617474079></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f100854617474079><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=3&mid=100854617474079>RE: monks..</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=3&mid=100854617474079#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=74412><span id=Sage>Corr</span></a>, <span id=Sage>Sage</span><br><span id=notbold>64 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sun, Dec 16th 6:42 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[5.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Well that is quite a pesimistic outlook on things.  I would of thought that after playing through 60 hellish levels you would atleast like your class ?<br><br>At the moment , i am 57 and i do not share any ill feelings about my class like you describe.  True , we do not do the most damage , but we ARE the 2nd most damaging melee class.  Rogues were ment for damage , thats just the plain fact so they will always do more damage than us.  And i don't have a clue where you got the idea that mages outdamage us.<br><br>Also , ofcourse , FD pulling can't be used everywhere , yet the monks are usually always chosen as the puller.  Our ability to control adds on pulls pretty much guarantee us that position.  Also , a good monk would be able to watch and time the casting message , so unless you have 3-4 casters on you , they shoulnt be much of a problem.  <br><br>Your statement about monks not being tanks are very misleading.  We may not have the high HP like the wariors , but we can , and do RIVAL them in the ac deparment.  Add to the fact that our avoidance capabilities totally own that of the warior , we can tank things fine in the many 50+ dungeons.  An example would be sebilis , we had the worse group combination you could think of and i was the tank.  We were still able to hold the Necro camp for a few hours.<br><br>Next time you go out xping , ask a rogue , or a warior what their ac is , im sure you will be suprised by what you hear.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sun Dec 16 18:53:05 2001</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Corr<br>Lvl 58 Master of the celestial fists<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=31645" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=31645</a><br></td></tr>
